name: Flappy Core (NateTheKnife)
description:
Flappy Core A Titanfall Fan Game Based on the work of Moy Parra (Titantoons)

How many points can you get? 10? 20? 999?!

The game is simple get through the pipes to earn a point

Controls:

Space: Jump

Left and right mouse button: Jump

Skins

There are 22 different skins
